These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, white, emerald, coral
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk, cola
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, september, january
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person who likes coral##6
 5. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
 8. the person who likes white is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
 9. the person who likes ivory is not the person drinking cola##6
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
12. the person who likes white is in an even position##4
13. the person who likes coral is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
14. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color    | ivory         | coral     | emerald     | white         |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday   | may       | march | january | september       |

