.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, november, october
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, american, indonesian, mexican
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, rose, begonia
 1. the indonesian is not to the right of the mexican##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the american##1
 5. the argentine is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the argentine##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | november          | june      | october      | april   |
| Nationality        | indonesian     | argentine | american | mexican      |
| Flower      | begonia | daisy    | bellflower  | rose |

