.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, almond-milk, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, cain, tiparillo, blend
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, aquamarine, purple, apricot
 1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 5. the person who likes pink is not the oliveros-smoker##6
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk  | water | tea | cola |
| Cigar   | cain  | oliveros      | blend | tiparillo        |
| Color     | pink | purple       | apricot    | aquamarine     |

