.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, pilot, architect, analyst
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, horse, mouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, tiparillo, dunhill, havana
 1. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 2. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
 4. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
 5. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is not the architect##6
 7. the software-developer is not the dunhill-smoker##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the software-developer##8
10. the havana-smoker is the architect##1
11. the havana-smoker is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Job         | architect       | software-developer | pilot  | analyst    |
| Pet   | horse       | mouse    | rabbit | lizard    |
| Cigar         | havana | baccarat   | dunhill   | tiparillo |

