.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, cola, milk
4 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, rat, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, classical, gospel, r&b
 1. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 2. the owner of the turtle is not the fan of classical##6
 3. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the owner of the turtle##7
 4. the fan of classical is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 6. the fan of gospel is the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 8. the fan of r&b is between the person drinking water and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
11. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage          | tea      | cola      | milk | water |
| Pet   | rat | hamster    | turtle | mouse     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | gospel | r&b  | classical |

