 1. the fisherman is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is not the designer##6
 3. the oliveros-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person eating blueberry##2
 4. the designer is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the fisherman is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is not the old-henry-smoker##6
 8. the photographer is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 9. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
11. the photographer is not to the left of the old-henry-smoker##8
12. the designer is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
13. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Job   | musician   | fisherman | designer        | photographer |
