1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing mah-jongg##7
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
4. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
6. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
7. the person playing domino is the ranch-style house##1
