 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
 4. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fonseca-smoker is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
 7. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 8. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
10. the person who likes lilac is not to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
11. the fonseca-smoker is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
13. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
14. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
