 6. the person who likes brown is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
11. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person eating cauliflower##6

.:: Answer ::.
